project_descr: RAF/08/005- Agri-Enterprise Development for Stimulating Rural Economies in Africa (UNDP Component of the Regional Joint Programme)- Songhai Project

outputs.output_descr: The Agri-Enterprise Development for Stimulating Rural Economies in Africa is a joint initiative between FAO, IFAD, ILO, UNDP and UNIDO, working in partnership with Songhai Centre, an international NGO based in Benin.
